title: PBS Space Time - DVD 2
description:
PBS Space Time DVD 2

English audio with English subtitles. Some videos might have translated subtitles in addition to the English language, or no subtitles at all.
Some subtitles are the unreviewed raws from YouTube, and might be very bad quality.

PBS Space Time directly from YouTube - check here for latest videos https://duckduckgo.com/?q=pbs+space+time&ia=videos

This is a custom made video DVD5 with the episodes from the official YouTube show, plus some extras. Enjoy your favourite physics talks offline, free from the distractions of YouTube and with a nice menu :) I hope you enjoy it!
